{
  "texts": [
    "We let one human expert read each comment and assign a sentiment label to it, and the label is verified by two other human experts.",
    "Only if the three experts reach a consensus, we include the comment along with its label into the testing dataset.",
    "We stop the labelling once we have 300 labelled comments with one-third for each category of sentiment.",
    "This will be our testing dataset.",
    "B. A-Learn Performance AnalysisA-Learn considers several widely used or latest LLMs as base models and then customizes them with our labelled adult learning dataset."
  ]
}